                 href=\"\/fr\/hypotheque\/programme-dachat-clef-en-main\">\n                                                        Programme d\u2019achat clef en main\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                \n                                                <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                        href=\"\/fr\/hypotheque\/pret-hypothecaire\">\n                                                        Pr\u00eat hypoth\u00e9caire\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <\/div>\n                                <\/div>\n\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Liens normaux -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/fr\/construction\">Notre \u00c9quipe<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/fr\/carrieres\">Carri\u00e8res<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/fr\/partenaires\">Partenaires<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/fr\/contact\">Contact<\/a><\/li>\n\n                <!-- CTA -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item ms-xl-2 my-3 my-xl-0\">\n                    <a href=\"\/fr\/contact\" class=\"btn vip-btn-gold rounded-pill px-4 py-2 w-100 w-xl-auto\">\n                        Consultation sans frais\n                    <\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Mobile: lien Services simple -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item d-xl-none\">\n                    <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/fr\/services\">Services<\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/nav>\n    \n    \n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0\">\n                <span class=\"badge bg-primary text-white mb-2\">Protection G\u00e9n\u00e9rale<\/span>\n                <h1 class=\"fw-bold mb-4\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">Assurance de dommages<\/h1>\n                <h4 class=\"text-muted mb-4\">Prot\u00e9gez votre avenir : Le r\u00f4le essentiel de la protection financi\u00e8re<\/h4>\n                <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin-bottom: 20px;\"><\/div>\n\n                <div class=\"text-dark text-justify mb-4\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\">\n                    <p>Dans un monde o\u00f9 l&#039;impr\u00e9vu fait partie de la vie, l&#039;assurance de dommages ne se limite pas \u00e0 un simple contrat : c&#039;est le pilier de votre protection financi\u00e8re. Elle joue un r\u00f4le absolument capital en vous offrant le filet de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 n\u00e9cessaire pour faire face aux sinistres et aux risques du quotidien.<\/p>\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled mt-3\">\n                        <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-car text-warning me-2\"><\/i> Assurance Auto et Habitation pour s\u00e9curiser vos biens personnels.<\/li>\n                        <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-store text-warning me-2\"><\/i> Assurance Commerciale pour prot\u00e9ger vos actifs et op\u00e9rations.<\/li>\n                        <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-user-tie text-warning me-2\"><\/i> Assurance Responsabilit\u00e9 Professionnelle pour d\u00e9fendre votre r\u00e9putation.<\/li>\n                    <\/ul>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div class=\"d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/rendez-vous\" class=\"btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 shadow-sm text-white fw-bold\">\n                        \u00c9valuation sans frais\n                    <\/a>\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/contact\" class=\"btn btn-outline-dark rounded-pill px-4 shadow-sm\">\n                        Contactez-nous\n                    <\/a>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/assuranceDommages\/jeune-couple-signant-contrat-location-tout-rencontrant-agent-immobilier-accent-est-mis-homme.jpg\"\n                    alt=\"Assurance dommages\" class=\"section-img rounded shadow hover-lift w-100 object-fit-cover\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-light\" id=\"auto\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-5 mb-4 mb-lg-0 order-2 order-lg-1\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/assuranceDommages\/assurance-auto.jpg\" alt=\"Auto\" class=\"img-fluid rounded shadow-lg\">\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-7 order-1 order-lg-2\">\n                <div class=\"ps-lg-4\">\n                    <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-2\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">Assurance Auto<\/h2>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted fw-bold\">Responsabilit\u00e9 Civile et Protection Tous Risques<\/p>\n\n                    <div class=\"row g-4 mt-3\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded shadow-sm h-100 border-start border-4 border-warning\">\n                                <h5 class=\"fw-bold\">La Responsabilit\u00e9 Civile (Obligatoire)<\/h5>\n                                <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">C&#039;est l&#039;\u00e9l\u00e9ment essentiel et obligatoire au Qu\u00e9bec. Elle assure votre protection financi\u00e8re en cas de dommages caus\u00e9s \u00e0 autrui. Bien que le minimum l\u00e9gal soit de 50 000 $, il est fortement recommand\u00e9 d&#039;opter pour 1 ou 2 millions $ pour une couverture ad\u00e9quate.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded shadow-sm h-100 border-start border-4 border-primary\">\n                                <h5 class=\"fw-bold\">L&#039;importance du &quot;Tous Risques&quot;<\/h5>\n                                <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Pour s\u00e9curiser votre propre investissement (votre v\u00e9hicule), l&#039;assurance &quot;Tous Risques&quot; est n\u00e9cessaire. Elle couvre les collisions, le vandalisme, le feu et les intemp\u00e9ries.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    \n                    <div class=\"mt-4 p-4 rounded text-white\" style=\"background-color: var(--vip-blue, #0E1030);\">\n                        <h5 class=\"fw-bold text-warning mb-2\">Arr\u00eatez de payer trop cher !<\/h5>\n                        <p class=\"mb-3 small opacity-75\">Nous magasinons pour vous aupr\u00e8s des assureurs de renom pour garantir le meilleur prix sur le march\u00e9.<\/p>\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assurance-auto\" class=\"btn btn-warning rounded-pill px-4 text-dark fw-bold\">\n                            En savoir plus <i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right ms-1\"><\/i>\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\" id=\"habitation\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-7\">\n                <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-2\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">Assurance Habitation<\/h2>\n                <p class=\"text-muted fw-bold\">Votre bouclier essentiel contre les impr\u00e9vus<\/p>\n                <p class=\"mb-4\">Au Qu\u00e9bec, c&#039;est un investissement fondamental pour prot\u00e9ger votre patrimoine, que vous soyez propri\u00e9taire ou locataire.<\/p>\n\n                <h5 class=\"fw-bold text-dark\">Ce que \u00e7a couvre :<\/h5>\n                <ul class=\"list-unstyled mb-4\">\n                    <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-fire text-danger me-2\"><\/i> Sinistres courants : Feu, vol, vandalisme.<\/li>\n                    <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-water text-info me-2\"><\/i> D\u00e9g\u00e2ts d&#039;eau : Ruptures de canalisation et d\u00e9bordements.<\/li>\n                    <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-user-shield text-success me-2\"><\/i> Responsabilit\u00e9 Civile : Si vous causez des dommages \u00e0 autrui (ex: votre bain d\u00e9borde chez le voisin).<\/li>\n                <\/ul>\n\n                <div class=\"row g-3\">\n                    <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                        <div class=\"p-3 border rounded h-100\">\n                            <h6 class=\"fw-bold text-primary\"><i class=\"fas fa-key me-2\"><\/i> Locataires<\/h6>\n                            <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Fortement recommand\u00e9e pour prot\u00e9ger vos biens et surtout votre responsabilit\u00e9 civile vis-\u00e0-vis du propri\u00e9taire.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                        <div class=\"p-3 border rounded h-100\">\n                            <h6 class=\"fw-bold text-primary\"><i class=\"fas fa-home me-2\"><\/i> Propri\u00e9taires<\/h6>\n                            <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">G\u00e9n\u00e9ralement obligatoire si vous avez une hypoth\u00e8que pour s\u00e9curiser l&#039;investissement de la banque.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <div class=\"mt-4\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assurance-habitation\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4\">\n                        En savoir plus <i class=\"fas fa-home ms-1\"><\/i>\n                    <\/a>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-5 mb-4 mb-lg-0 mt-4 mt-lg-0\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assets\/img\/assuranceDommages\/assurance-habitation.jpg\" alt=\"Habitation\" class=\"img-fluid rounded shadow-lg\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-light\" id=\"commercial\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h2 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color:var(--primary-color);\">Protection des Entreprises<\/h2>\n            <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin: 15px auto;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"row g-5\">\n            \n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n                    <div class=\"card-header bg-dark text-white p-4\">\n                        <h4 class=\"mb-0 fw-bold\"><i class=\"fas fa-building me-2 text-warning\"><\/i> Assurance Commerciale<\/h4>\n                        <small class=\"text-white-50\">Le pilier de la prosp\u00e9rit\u00e9 de votre entreprise<\/small>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"card-body p-4\">\n                        <p class=\"card-text\">Que vous soyez travailleur autonome, d\u00e9taillant ou manufacturier, l&#039;assurance commerciale est la solution tout-en-un pour s\u00e9curiser votre investissement et garantir la continuit\u00e9 de vos activit\u00e9s.<\/p>\n                        <h6 class=\"fw-bold mt-3\">Pourquoi est-ce indispensable ?<\/h6>\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled small text-muted\">\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-check text-success me-2\"><\/i> S\u00e9curit\u00e9 Financi\u00e8re : \u00c9vite les co\u00fbts exorbitants li\u00e9s aux poursuites ou dommages.<\/li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-check text-success me-2\"><\/i> Continuit\u00e9 des Affaires : Couvre les frais fixes et salaires en cas d&#039;arr\u00eat (incendie, etc.).<\/li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-check text-success me-2\"><\/i> Protection des Actifs : B\u00e2timents, \u00e9quipements, inventaire et donn\u00e9es.<\/li>\n                        <\/ul>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"card-footer bg-white border-0 p-4 pt-0\">\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assurance-commerciale\" class=\"btn btn-primary w-100 py-2 fw-bold rounded-pill\">\n                            En savoir plus\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            \n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n                    <div class=\"card-header bg-primary text-white p-4\">\n                        <h4 class=\"mb-0 fw-bold\"><i class=\"fas fa-briefcase me-2\"><\/i> Assurance Responsabilit\u00e9 Professionnelle (E&amp;O)<\/h4>\n                        <small class=\"text-white-50\">La protection essentielle de votre expertise<\/small>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"card-body p-4\">\n                        <p class=\"card-text\">Aussi appel\u00e9e &quot;Erreurs et Omissions&quot;, c&#039;est le bouclier financier pour tout professionnel offrant des conseils ou services intellectuels.<\/p>\n                        <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                            <span class=\"badge bg-light text-dark border me-1\">Consultants<\/span>\n                            <span class=\"badge bg-light text-dark border me-1\">Ing\u00e9nieurs<\/span>\n                            <span class=\"badge bg-light text-dark border\">Comptables<\/span>\n                        <\/div>\n                        <h6 class=\"fw-bold mt-3\">Ce que \u00e7a couvre sp\u00e9cifiquement :<\/h6>\n                        <ul class=\"list-unstyled small text-muted\">\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt text-primary me-2\"><\/i> Erreurs, omissions ou fautes de n\u00e9gligence dans votre travail.<\/li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-gavel text-primary me-2\"><\/i> Frais de d\u00e9fense juridique (avocats), souvent tr\u00e8s co\u00fbteux.<\/li>\n                            <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-money-bill text-primary me-2\"><\/i> Montant du r\u00e8glement si vous \u00eates tenu responsable.<\/li>\n                        <\/ul>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"card-footer bg-white border-0 p-4 pt-0\">\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.ca\/assurance-responsabilite-professionnelle\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary w-100 py-2 fw-bold rounded-pill\">\n                            En savoir plus\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- \n<section class=\"py-5 position-relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, #1a1d50 100%);\">\n    <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -50px; left: -50px; width: 200px; height: 200px